title: #75 - Sub Urban on Collabing with Bella Poarch & Valkyrae
itunes:title: #75 - Sub Urban on Collabing with Bella Poarch & Valkyrae
description: On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast, music artist Sub Urban comes onto the show as a guest to talk about his reaction to his single Cradles blow up on TikTok, working with Bella Poarch and Valkyrae, his new single Paramour, and more!
